name: cube-icon
readme:
# cube-icon

3D CSS cube icons

Usage:

    var CubeIcon = require('cube-icon')
    document.body.appendChild(CubeIcon({left:..., front:..., top:...}).container); // pass image URLs

Example (run `npm start`):
